data.text: The Boston Leadership Reception is an opportunity for CEOs and business leaders to connect and to continue to strengthen the American-Australian alliance. Nick Greiner, Australian Consul General, New York, will provide remarks. Thank you to Arjun Goyal, Vida Ventures for generously hosting.
